newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 66 OF MARCH 6, 1997.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 66 OF MARCH 6, 1997.

text.p: * Council Regulation (EC) No 390/97 of 20 December 1996 fixing, for certain fish stocks and groups of fish stocks, the total allowable catches for 1997 and certain conditions under which they may be fished
Council Regulation (EC) No 391/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down, for 1997, certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of Norway

Council Regulation (EC) No 392/97 of 20 December 1996 allocating, for 1997, certain catch quotas between Member States for vessels fishing in the Norwegian exclusive economic zone and the fishing zone around Jan Mayen

Council Regulation (EC) No 393/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down, for 1997, certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of the Faroe Islands
Council Regulation (EC) No 394/97 of 20 December 1996 allocating, for 1997, certain catch quotas between Member States for vessels fishing in Faroese waters
Council Regulation (EC) No 395/97 of 20 December 1996 allocating, for 1997, Community catch quotas in Greenland waters
Council Regulation (EC) No 396/97 of 20 December 1996 allocating, for 1997, catch quotas between Member States for vessels fishing in Icelandic waters
Council Regulation (EC) No 397/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down for 1997 certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of Estonia
Council Regulation (EC) No 398/97 of 20 December 1996 allocating for 1997 catch quotas between Member States for vessels fishing in Estonian waters

Council Regulation (EC) No 399/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down for 1997 certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of the Latvia

Council Regulation (EC) No 401/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down, for 1997, certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of the Lithuania

Council Regulation (EC) No 403/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down for 1997 certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable to vessels flying the flag of Poland

Council Regulation (EC) No 405/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down for 1997 certain measures for the conservation and management of fishery resources applicable in vessels flying the flag of certain non-member countries in the 200-nautical-mile zone off the coast of the French department of Guiana

Council Regulation (EC) No 406/97 of 20 December 1996 laying down for 1997 certain conservation and management measures for fishery resources in the Regulatory Area as defined in the Convention on Future Multilateral Cooperation in the North-West Atlantic Fisheries
